Class WInvisibleContainer

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.bordertech.wcomponents.AbstractWComponent

        • com.github.bordertech.wcomponents.AbstractNamingContextContainer

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Container, MutableContainer, NamingContextable, WComponent, WebComponent, Serializable

    public class WInvisibleContainer
extends AbstractMutableContainer

    This container is used as a marker for some special cases, where we want to skip normal WComponent life-cycle processes.

    It is always invisible.

    Since:
    1.0.0
    Author:
    Yiannis Paschalidis
